{"tid":2446201,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"閃燈襲警案　手足冇雷射筆","createTime":"2021-03-14T09:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T06:09:17.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"51d929165524fbd9b1b5d80759265a9e190c3fc9","tid":2446201,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cswpower/posts/2865749140362337\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcswpower%2Fposts%2F2865749140362337&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfAbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=2ece0299\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cswpower/posts/2865749140362337</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：長沙灣社區發展力量 - 長社力<br />\n<br />\n[閃燈襲警案][手足冇雷射筆]<br />\n<br />\n由於好多市民都關心案情, 但唔同媒體用唔同嘅形容詞, 我哋喺度簡單解釋一下。<br />\n<br />\n今次案件裏面, 警方喺手足身上面搜出一支電筒, 呢一支電筒係綠色燈光嘅。 並唔係大家理解嘅鐳射筆。<br />\n<br />\n手足當日正同朋友交收電筒, 係西九龍中心八樓food court 開啟電筒 約0.5秒作測試 睇下係咪運作正常。 案件中嘅警員, 事後就係因為呢0.5秒嘅電筒餘暉, 警員報稱受襲。<br />\n<br />\n而當時警員喺綠色燈光出現之後幾分鐘, 手足用電話攝影空姐牛肉飯時, 才上前以影相為由作出拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n#特此解釋<br />\n#閃燈襲警案 #案中冇雷射筆出現過<br />\n#紙紮警依然係紙紮 #閃燈依然係閃燈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uEn3oJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuEn3oJ3.png&h=f6b453a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2abac94beadbbd8a10dd537352f38727af9cbc94","tid":2446201,"uid":393145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e73e83f21320802e88db71bd13abf0f2cfcc4b","tid":2446201,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"狗果支就真係laser gun勒"},{"pid":"d538df740520324d571f369a55c8cac5a4ef65d3","tid":2446201,"uid":275384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets